Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.02,0:00:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name's Conan Edogawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.52,0:00:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,High school student Shinichi was forced\Nto take a drug that shrunk him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.60,0:00:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although smaller, my mind remains\Nthat of a sharp detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.39,0:00:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's case is a two-part story\Naboard a luxury liner!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.57,0:00:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think you can tell who did it\Njust from Part 1?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.53,0:00:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's always only one truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.74,0:00:21.19,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first end of the century in 100 years{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.83,0:00:27.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When told to cry, I laughed instead{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.03,0:00:39.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first end of the century\Nin a long, long time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.18,0:00:45.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're leaping into a wide open world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.17,0:00:52.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The things I tried to\Nunderstand as a child{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.34,0:00:58.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}remain a mystery even as an adult{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.89,0:01:04.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm neither a hotshot\Nnor especially great{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.89,0:01:11.03,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All I understand is\Nthe pounding of my heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.19,0:01:16.92,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's neither an answer nor the truth{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.20,0:01:23.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All I have faith in is\Nthe pounding of my heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.29,0:01:28.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That and nothing else {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.79,0:01:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Luxury Liner Murders, Part 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.09,0:02:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a beautiful view!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.22,0:02:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We sure were lucky!\NI was worried for a while there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.81,0:02:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.68,0:02:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He forgot what time\Nour return ship left,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.77,0:02:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we got to ride on\Nthis big one instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.94,0:02:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a good thing this ship\Njust happened to stop at the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.53,0:02:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We would've been stranded out\Nthere for 3 days if it hadn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.62,0:02:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wonder what kind of people\Nwould reserve a ship like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.29,0:02:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.17,0:02:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.38,0:02:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking about my parents\Nwho died in an accident last year...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.18,0:02:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish they could've seen me\Nall dressed up today...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.27,0:02:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All dressed up?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.39,0:02:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong, Natsue?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.31,0:02:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takeshi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.06,0:02:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The two of us were married today!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.36,0:02:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Married?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.90,0:03:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We had our ceremony this morning\Non Hatamoto Island,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.36,0:03:04.78,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoichi's 2nd daughter Hatamoto Natsue (22)\NNatsue's Husband Hatamoto Takeshi (24)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.86,0:03:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the same island you were on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.58,0:03:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why did you have it on the island?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.29,0:03:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The majority of the island\Nbelongs to the Hatamoto family.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.13,0:03:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We honor generations\Nof our ancestors there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.96,0:03:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Hatamoto family tradition to\Nhold wedding ceremonies on the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.59,0:03:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.68,0:03:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We reserved this boat for ourselves,\Nso what are strangers doing on it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.48,0:03:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.48,0:03:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They appeared to be stranded, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.57,0:03:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you go over my head!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.44,0:03:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must think pretty highly of yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.44,0:03:46.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Mariko's husband Hatamoto Kitaro (47)\NHead of the Hatamoto family Hatamoto Go (72)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you're making decisions without approval.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, of course I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.70,0:03:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.33,0:03:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been in a bad mood\Nsince the ceremony today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.33,0:03:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, after he ate my food...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.17,0:03:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle Joji!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.42,0:04:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew he hated Western-style food,\Nbut I had no idea he'd get that angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.09,0:04:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You call this food?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems my skills still aren't up to par.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:10.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Second son of the Hatamoto family\NHatamoto Joji (41)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.81,0:04:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was really delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, lady-killer...\NWhat's with the flower?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.52,0:04:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Natsue put it there on\Nthe way back from the ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's always been my dream\Nsince I was a little girl
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.07,0:04:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to give my beloved this flower\Nthat only grows on that island.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad it wasn't me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.99,0:04:32.08,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitaro's only son\NHatamoto Ichiro (21)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like father, like son!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you going to let\Nhim pretend to be an artist?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.84,0:04:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're his father,\Ntalk some sense into him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell him to give up his hopeless dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.88,0:04:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takeshi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.01,0:04:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need a word with you!\NCome to my room later!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.64,0:04:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.64,0:04:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just have patience, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.61,0:05:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't long for this world--\Nhe'll be gone soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.49,0:05:10.12,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Eldest Hatamoto daughter,\NKitaro's wife, Hatamoto Mariko (43)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.49,0:05:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when he is, nearly all of the\NHatamoto fortune will be yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.12,0:05:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be so sure about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.83,0:05:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.42,0:05:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akie-san! Do you know\Nsomething I don't?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.96,0:05:22.17,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoichi's daughter & Natsue's sister\NHatamoto Akie (26)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be too shocked when you hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.59,0:05:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible! That can't be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.60,0:05:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like Grandfather's\Ngoing to make the announcement
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.18,0:05:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when we get back to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:39.77,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Akie's husband Hatamoto Tatsuo (26)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.19,0:05:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NDoes he even know we're up to\Nour necks in debt over here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.61,0:05:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have 24 hours until\Nthe ship arrives in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We simply have to\Ndo something before then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:05:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me, Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.38,0:06:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.88,0:06:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to disturb you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.92,0:06:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was an exceptional speech\Nyou gave at the wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.59,0:06:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what I would expect\Nof the man whom Natsue chose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.39,0:06:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.68,0:06:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scratching your cheeks\Nwhen you're embarrassed...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.98,0:06:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.23,0:06:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like your father, Zaiki Isao!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.82,0:06:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Falsify your family registry all\Nyou want, you still cannot fool me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.24,0:06:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've known all this time\Nthat you joined the company
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.83,0:06:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and got close to Natsue\Njust to avenge your father!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it you're after?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.62,0:06:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Money?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.38,0:06:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or my life, perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.34,0:06:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?\NWhy won't you speak?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.01,0:06:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.80,0:06:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are the main members\Nof the Hatamoto family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:07:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So all of these people\Nwent to your wedding?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.73,0:07:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! All nine of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.52,0:07:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,excluding my late parents\NShoichi and Miyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.44,0:07:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Takeshi-san is rather late...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. He still hasn't come\Nback from Grandfather's room...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.41,0:07:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they're discussing some\Nunder-the-table business!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.92,0:07:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.63,0:07:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.55,0:07:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad not here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.55,0:07:34.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hatamoto family butler Suzuki Kenji (64)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.55,0:07:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, though I am certain he will be here shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.26,0:07:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late, Ichiro-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.22,0:07:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you make sure to wash your hands?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.68,0:07:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.68,0:07:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say! Do you have a boyfriend, Ran-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.23,0:07:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not, she's still a kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.94,0:07:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.44,0:07:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have you know\Nthere is someone I like!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.99,0:07:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Conan-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.07,0:07:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.99,0:07:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he like?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.83,0:08:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he's really smart, good at soccer,\Ndependable, and cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.67,0:08:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you acting\Nso embarrassed about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.09,0:08:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he's an even better\Ndetective than my dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.88,0:08:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean your father's a--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? I didn't tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.76,0:08:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad's a detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.44,0:08:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it a secret from my grandfather!\NHe hates detectives!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He says that people who pry\Ninto others' affairs are despicable!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.49,0:08:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right, at least\Nin old man Kogoro's case.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.33,0:08:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir? Your seat is ready, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.04,0:08:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A flower?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.42,0:08:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takeshi-san! You're really late!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.76,0:08:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I was thinking\Nabout some things in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.93,0:09:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright? You look pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.85,0:09:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? What happened to your flower?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange.\NWhere could I have lost it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.44,0:09:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to disturb you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.86,0:09:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is waiting for you--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.66,0:09:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whose voice was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.07,0:09:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The butler's!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.53,0:09:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It came from Dad's room!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened, Suzuki-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.84,0:09:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late. He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.89,0:09:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.97,0:09:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandfather!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.43,0:09:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.64,0:09:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone stay out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.39,0:09:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody's to enter this room\Nuntil I say it's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.27,0:09:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would seem that 40 or 50 minutes\Nhave passed since Gozo's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.15,0:10:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were the one\Nwho found him, Suzuki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.07,0:10:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.74,0:10:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where were you 40 to 50 minutes ago,\Naround 8:00 PM?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.08,0:10:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was getting things\Nready for dinner at 8:00,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I was in the dining room\Nthe entire time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.54,0:10:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did see Suzuki-san working\Nin a hurry around the tables!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.09,0:10:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The door to this room was locked\Nwhen you found the body, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.81,0:10:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What ways are there to lock the door?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.98,0:10:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can be locked from the inside,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.31,0:10:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you need this key\Nto lock it from the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.10,0:10:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this window doesn't open, so it's\Nimpossible to sneak into the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.48,0:10:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words,\Nthis room was impregnable!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.74,0:10:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impregnable?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying that my grandfather\Ncommitted suicide?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.62,0:10:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.37,0:10:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it was a suicide, then there's\Nsomething important missing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.42,0:10:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.17,0:10:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He died of blood loss after\Nbeing stabbed in the abdomen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.84,0:11:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the knife used to do it\Nis nowhere to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.18,0:11:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure it wasn't a dagger\Nmade of ice or anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.05,0:11:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mystery novels are full of things\Nthat melt away and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.89,0:11:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would someone seriously commit suicide\Nwith something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.65,0:11:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet this is more of his harassment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.32,0:11:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wanted to torment us by making\Nevery Hatamoto here seem suspect!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.03,0:11:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He hated everyone\Nin the family, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.74,0:11:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone except Natsue-san, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.66,0:11:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akie!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.16,0:11:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't put it past the old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.87,0:11:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's decided! It was a suicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.67,0:11:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was a murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.75,0:11:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.46,0:11:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And an extremely simple one, at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.92,0:11:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.09,0:11:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, take a close look\Nat the doorframe!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.30,0:11:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See the blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.01,0:11:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the door was closed\Nwhen he committed suicide,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,none of his blood\Ncould have landed there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.31,0:11:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's more natural to think that\Nhe was stabbed while the door was open.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.27,0:12:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! Somebody stabbed Gozo\Nthe instant he left the room!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.32,0:12:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then who locked the door?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.62,0:12:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No clue...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.45,0:12:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you sure you're a detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! It was Mr. Gozo himself\Nwho locked the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.22,0:12:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone stabbed him outside the room\Nand then kept coming for him,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.56,0:12:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so he locked himself inside\Nto escape his attacker!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.98,0:12:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then he ran\Nout of strength and died!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.73,0:12:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That would make the most sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.73,0:12:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a great detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.07,0:12:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute! That means everyone\Nhad an opportunity to kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.74,0:12:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The murder took place\Nat approximately 8:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.87,0:12:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran, Conan, Natsue-san,\Nand I were at our table since 7:30,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.25,0:12:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so none of us could have done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.75,0:12:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same can be said for Suzuki-san,\Nwho was near our table at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.84,0:13:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, since the killer\Nwasn't in the dining room at the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.17,0:13:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it was one of you seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.44,0:13:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you entered the room, did you\Nnotice anything out of the ordinary?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.65,0:13:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing in particular...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.90,0:13:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, now that you mention it, I found\Nthis flower in front of the door...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.03,0:13:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flower?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.32,0:13:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the flower I put on\NTakeshi-san's jacket!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.83,0:13:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, you were really\Nlate coming to the dining room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.79,0:13:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I was just thinking\Nabout things in my room...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.09,0:13:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try to deny it, Takeshi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.63,0:13:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I happened to hear you\Nand Father shouting in his room!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.85,0:13:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was going to faint
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:14:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when I heard that you're\Nactually the son of Zaiki Isao!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.74,0:14:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's Zaiki Isao?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.24,0:14:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He committed suicide when Gozo\Ntook over his company 10 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.08,0:14:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One year later,\Nhis wife died of an illness,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.21,0:14:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and their only son was apparently\Nplaced in an institution.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.80,0:14:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that that was Takeshi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.26,0:14:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true, Takeshi-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.06,0:14:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takeshi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.81,0:14:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'm Zaiki Takeshi,\Nson of Zaiki Isao!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.69,0:14:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.86,0:14:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Got close to Natsue-san\Nso you could avenge your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.32,0:14:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You decided to become a member\Nof the Hatamoto family
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.74,0:14:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and wait for the chance to kill Gozo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.25,0:15:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then tonight, you did just that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I didn't kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.42,0:15:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsue! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.63,0:15:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had you pegged as\Na pretty staunch fellow,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.39,0:15:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it looks like I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.68,0:15:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Joji-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.47,0:15:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta be an idiot to drop\Nyour flower at the crime scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.89,0:15:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't, I lost my flower somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.77,0:15:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are wiped blood stains\Non the outside carpet...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.90,0:15:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, was that flower\Nreally here on the floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.11,0:15:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's right, little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.58,0:15:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.70,0:15:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bread crumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.58,0:15:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bread crumb lying\Nin a pool of blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.33,0:15:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's it mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.25,0:15:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Mr. Butler.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.21,0:15:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was there bread during the\Nwedding banquet this afternoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.34,0:15:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But of course--it was an\Nextravagant French meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.77,0:16:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Joji-sama made it all himself.\NHe runs his own French restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.15,0:16:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did everyone eat it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.56,0:16:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Everyone but Gozo-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.65,0:16:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He loathed Western-style food.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.86,0:16:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said that just looking\Nat bread would make him nauseous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.32,0:16:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Joji-san's a chef, he has\Nkitchen knives of his own, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.29,0:16:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally. Chefs like him\Nalways own their own set.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.83,0:16:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come now, children shouldn't\Npry into other people's business.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.05,0:16:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.01,0:16:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool off in this storeroom for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.18,0:16:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open up! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.81,0:16:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid, you murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.85,0:16:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're giving you to the police\Nthe minute we arrive in Tokyo tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.85,0:16:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Better get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.73,0:16:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His motive and all the evidence is\Nmore than enough, right, Detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.11,0:16:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He had more than enough motive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.99,0:16:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if his fingerprints are found\Non the murder weapon, it's in the bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.37,0:16:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.45,0:16:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.41,0:17:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go, little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.91,0:17:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.87,0:17:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are lucky, Mariko.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.58,0:17:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that Takeshi-san\Nhas killed the old man,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.55,0:17:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he'll never make that stupid\Nannouncement about his inheritance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.68,0:17:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.01,0:17:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now the Hatamoto Group\Nwill belong to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.97,0:17:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the husband of his eldest daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.60,0:17:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you can draw as much as you want,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.60,0:17:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,now that your grandfather's dead,\NIchiro-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.81,0:17:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And eventually, you too will\Nbecome the Hatamoto Group's--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.06,0:17:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really want that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.03,0:17:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you ain't thinkin' of monopolizing\Nthe guy's inheritance, are ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.49,0:17:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! All you\Ngrandchildren will get--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.41,0:17:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you not talk about money\Non the night of our father's death?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.16,0:17:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you to talk? You left\Nthe family to go be a chef!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.75,0:17:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that Father flat out refused you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:17:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when you asked to borrow\Nmoney for your restaurant!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.35,0:18:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanted his money too!\NSo be grateful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.47,0:18:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.93,0:18:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm extremely sorry to say this,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.90,0:18:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but your father wrote up a will
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.90,0:18:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just in case something\Nwas to happen to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.86,0:18:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.20,0:18:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it will be read at the\Nmain office in the next few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.74,0:18:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean--?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.28,0:18:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of his fortune goes to--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.66,0:18:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsue?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.66,0:18:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsue?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.75,0:18:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.62,0:18:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And leadership of the Hatamoto Group\Nis to be given to the man
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.04,0:18:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that Natsue-san chose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.92,0:18:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.84,0:18:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Then what the hell\Ndid I marry Akie for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.26,0:18:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you only married me\Nto get my dad's money!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.18,0:18:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Why else would I live\Nwith a tight-fisted bitch like you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.69,0:18:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you to talk?!\NYou're just a worthless musician!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.56,0:18:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go and get a real job!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.91,0:19:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsue-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.66,0:19:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.16,0:19:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing, just thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About Takeshi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I trusted him...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.81,0:19:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he only married me so\Nhe could kill my grandfather!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.06,0:19:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never trust anyone again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I trust him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.70,0:19:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My gut feeling tells me\Nthat he's not a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.50,0:19:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one you chose, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.25,0:19:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He couldn't possibly be a bad person!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.50,0:19:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.84,0:20:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.18,0:20:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you hear\Nanything strange just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.47,0:20:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear anything, Natsue-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.97,0:20:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.89,0:20:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I did hear something!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.06,0:20:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sound of something\Nfalling into the water
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.85,0:20:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then a weird thud\Nfrom the deck below!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.48,0:20:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.19,0:20:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Conan-kun! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.03,0:20:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's gotten into you two--?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.75,0:20:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cause of death was\Nmost likely brain damage
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.34,0:20:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,caused by a blow to the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.59,0:20:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Judging from the wound,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.84,0:20:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the murder weapon was a\Nsteel pipe or something similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.97,0:20:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would do something this terrible?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.85,0:20:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me Takeshi's struck again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.02,0:20:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible. He was locked in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.35,0:20:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.23,0:21:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The door's unlocked!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.15,0:21:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.95,0:21:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.21,0:22:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wasn't in the storeroom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.01,0:22:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We most certainly locked him inside,\Nbut he's nowhere to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.13,0:22:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Takeshi was the one who\Nkilled Father and Tatsuo-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.18,0:22:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The thud that Conan heard
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.14,0:23:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was probably the sound of\Nthe killer hitting Tatsuo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.82,0:23:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The splash he heard
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.94,0:23:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was either the sound of the murder weapon\Nbeing thrown overboard, or...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.15,0:23:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the sound of the killer\Njumping into the water
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.12,0:23:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after running out of places to hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.04,0:23:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takeshi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.37,0:23:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, there's still\Na high possibility
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.33,0:23:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that there's a killer aboard this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.54,0:23:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all withdraw to\Nthe dining room for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.84,0:23:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying he could\Nbe trying to kill me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.92,0:23:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.51,0:23:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His motive for murder was to\Nexact revenge on Hatamoto Gozo,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.30,0:23:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who drove his father\Nto suicide 10 years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.06,0:23:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But for all we know...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.68,0:23:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...he could be trying to kill\Neveryone in the Hatamoto family!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.80,0:24:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that you have another man!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.64,0:24:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who wants\Nthe inheritance the most!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.39,0:24:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Ichiro was mad at him
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.73,0:24:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for tearing up his prize-winning drawing!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.18,0:24:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.69,0:24:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My leg!
